<C>__{jacob}
<D>__{what happened to him?}
<C>__{kenny}
<D>__{he pissed off the wrong guy off. jeff is totally fucked right now.}
<C>__{jacob}
<D>__{good.}
<C>__{kenny}
<D>__{don't come back here ever again.}
